data.description: Immaculate Home!  Seller has totally renovated the interior of this home.  You'll be amazed.  Just beautiful!  New flooring, dry wall, insulation, counter tops, cabinets, bathrooms, walk-in shower, ceiling fans, light fixtures, carpet, luxury vinyl floors, new HVAC, windows, etc.  All new appliances.  Just name it, it's been done!  Detached 2-Car Garage.  All this on 5.10 acres +/- in lovely Charlotte County, VA.  Make your appointment to see this home today!
